  <brief_title>Emergence Delirium and Recovery Time in Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>Emergence Delirium and Recovery Time in Children: a Randomized Trial to Compare Total Intravenous Anesthesia With Propofol to Inhalational Sevoflurane Anesthesia for Ambulatory Dental Surgery</official_title>
