  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this study, inhalation anesthesia procedure and intravenous anesthesia method will be
      compared in terms of emergence delirium and recovery time in children who are scheduled for
      dental treatment under general anesthesia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Pediatric Anesthesia Early Delirium Scale (PAEDS) will be used to evaluate postoperative
      emergence delirium.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
